sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Codex
    participant M as carher-her-mcp
    participant B as Bridge/Admin
    participant P as Her Gateway Proxy
    participant H as Target Her(OpenClaw)
    participant F as Feishu/Tools

    C->>M: her_send(her_uid, prompt)
    M->>B: POST /api/her-rpc/sessions
    B->>B: 校验 MCP token + her 权限
    B->>P: route her_uid -> carher-{uid}-svc
    P->>H: OpenClaw Gateway / A2A request
    H->>F: 需要时使用飞书身份/skills/tools
    F-->>H: 工具结果
    H-->>P: streamed result / final result
    P-->>B: session events
    B-->>M: result / session_id
    M-->>C: tool result
